items.title: Amazon and Apple earnings coverage, Eli Lilly: What to Watch
items.description: Market Domination Overtime hosts Julie Hyman and Josh Lipton preview several of the biggest stories and reports due out tomorrow, Thursday, May 1, including Apple (AAPL) and Amazon's (AMZN) respective quarterly earnings results alongside Eli Lilly (LLY), Mastercard (MA), McDonald's (MCD), and CVS Health (CVS). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
